description:
Watch until the end 🤯
-
-
Clip from last weeks GFL update. This literally blew my mind but I’m so happy they told me because it lead to this weeks video. 😢
-
-
I didn’t expect to cry yesterday but the pain was so real. The biggest emotion I felt was the anguish of leaving these souls behind and feeling guilty for “getting away”. 😔
-
-
I had such a deep healing in my sacral and solar plexus. I know because I felt so extremely nauseous the entire time I channeled. I was such a mess I didn’t even know if I could get through the video. 
-
-
When my wife saw how distraught I was, she told me “it’s okay babe, our children will be safe” and in that moment I realized that yes, the children of the future will be safe because we are here now... putting an end to it. ❤️
-
-
Remember, the most important part of that video is the understanding that you can do something to change this, to stop it. 💪🏼
-
-
Your thoughts create this reality. If we all collectively project a future where all children are free and the cabal is taken down then we are doing our part xox 🧬😌
-
-
Protesting is great, but it can also be a distraction within the limitations of 3D. Conscious projection & creation is clear and always in 5D so it happens instantly xox 🙌🏼🌍
-
-
Thank you all for supporting me and holding space for this info ❤️🌈
